key.value: progress.progressbar should be the progressbar element
progress.video should be the video_div element
'video.loadstart' event should callback the preload function with 'true' arg value
'video.seeking' event should callback the prelaod function with 'true' arg value
'video.loadedmetadata' event should callback the prelaod function with 'false' arg value
'video.seeked' event should callback the prelaod function with 'false' arg value
'video.progress' event with no length computable should callback the prelaod function with 'true' arg value
'video.progress' event with length computable should callback the tick function
